parameters.content:
## ✅ **🔹 Section 1: Trigger & Prepare**

**Nodes:**
1️⃣ `Weekly Territory Check` *(Schedule Trigger)*
2️⃣ `Prepare Request Params` *(Edit Fields)*

**💡 What it does:**

* ⏰ **Weekly Trigger**: The automation starts **automatically** on a set schedule — e.g., every Monday at 6 AM — so you don’t need to remember to run it.
* 📝 **Prepare Request**: This step **sets up the input** — like choosing which regions to scrape, date filters, or any special parameters you want the scraper to use.

**✨ Why it’s powerful for you:**

* You never forget to update your data.
* Anyone can **adjust input** (e.g., change region) **without touching the rest of the workflow**.
* Perfect for **zero-code team edits**.

---

## ✅ **🔹 Section 2: Smart Data Collection & Parsing**

**Nodes:**
3️⃣ `Run Bright Data Scraper` *(AI Agent)*
— uses ⏬

* `Bright Data MCP Tool` *(MCP Client)*
* `LLM Prompt Handler` *(OpenAI Chat Model)*
* `Fix/Format Scraper Output` *(Auto-fixing Output Parser)*
* `Validation Assistant` *(OpenAI Chat Model1)*
* `Final Output Formatter` *(Structured Output Parser)*

**💡 What it does:**

* 🤖 The **AI Agent** talks to the **Bright Data MCP Tool** to **scrape live data** from your target sites.
* 🧠 The **LLM Prompt Handler** helps the AI figure out what pages to crawl, what data to look for, and how to handle tricky websites.
* 🧹 The **Auto-fixer & Parsers** make sure your scraped data is always **clean JSON**, so you never get errors in the next steps.

**✨ Why it’s powerful for you:**

* This section handles all the **dirty work** of web scraping & fixing messy data.
* You **don’t write code or worry about site changes** — the agent + model fix issues automatically.
* If a page changes, the AI adjusts how it scrapes, so you’re not stuck fixing broken scrapers every week.

---

## ✅ **🔹 Section 3: Process, Save & Notify**

**Nodes:**
4️⃣ `Split Stores to Items` *(Code)*
5️⃣ `Update Regional Data Sheet` *(Google Sheets)*
6️⃣ `Send Notification Email` *(Gmail)*

**💡 What it does:**

* ⚙️ The `Split Stores to Items` node **unwraps** the single big output from the scraper → breaks it into **one item per store** so you can work with them individually.
* 📊 The `Update Regional Data Sheet` node **writes each store’s info** into Google Sheets — creating a clean, always-up-to-date record of all your stores & their sales.
* 📧 The `Send Notification Email` node **alerts you automatically** if anything needs attention — for example, “Hey, Region North has 20% higher load than Region South. Reassign recommended!”

## 🎯 **Your Workflow: Territory Performance Analyzer & Reassigner**

**✨ Purpose:**
Every week, this automation **scrapes fresh regional sales data**, splits it cleanly, saves it to a tracking sheet, and sends a smart email update if anything needs your attention — **all without you doing a thing!**

---

## ✅ **🔹 Section 1: Trigger & Prepare**

## ✅ **🔹 Section 3: Process, Save & Notify**

**Nodes:**
4️⃣ `Split Stores to Items` *(Code)*
5️⃣ `Update Regional Data Sheet` *(Google Sheets)*
6️⃣ `Send Notification Email` *(Gmail)*

**💡 What it does:**

* ⚙️ The `Split Stores to Items` node **unwraps** the single big output from the scraper → breaks it into **one item per store** so you can work with them individually.
* 📊 The `Update Regional Data Sheet` node **writes each store’s info** into Google Sheets — creating a clean, always-up-to-date record of all your stores & their sales.
* 📧 The `Send Notification Email` node **alerts you automatically** if anything needs attention — for example, “Hey, Region North has 20% higher load than Region South. Reassign recommended!”

**✨ Why it’s powerful for you:**

* You get **fresh, structured data** to review any time.
* No manual copy/paste → your team sees **live performance trends**.
* Automated emails keep your sales leads or managers in the loop without extra work.

---

## 🎉 **🔑 How a Beginner Can Use This**

✅ **No coding:** Everything runs with prebuilt nodes.
✅ **Flexible:** Change your schedule, filters, or regions without breaking the flow.
✅ **Scalable:** Easily add more stores, new regions, or extra tools — e.g., auto-publish to Airtable or a dashboard.
✅ **Fully Automated:** Wake up Monday → check your sheet → know exactly where to adjust territories.

---

## ✅ **🌟 Visual Summary with Icons**

| Section                | Steps                                              | Icon     |
| ---------------------- | -------------------------------------------------- | -------- |
| **1️⃣ Trigger & Prep** | 🕒 Weekly schedule → 📝 set scrape parameters      | ⏰ ✏️     |

| **3️⃣ Process & Act**  | 🔗 Split items → 📊 Save to Sheets → 📧 Send email | ⚙️ 📊 📧 |

---

## 🗂️ **Result:**

**Zero-hassle, fully automated territory management**, designed for **non-coders**, **sales ops**, or any small business owner.
